::Killfest/Scyther/Incarcinator::

Killfest nods and turns to Darkfate. "I'll go, but most of my bots 
don't have flight capability, and this is quite aways out to sea. Do 
you have any jetpacks that my bots can use?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Scyther's shuttle stops near Incarcinator to pick him up and then 
heads toward earth. (At least it does if Pinsir is there. If he's 
not, it goes to pick up Pinsir. I kinda lost track of this).
